{
  "id": "adv_event_2207_01_03",
  "title": "初めての\n食事会",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さくらとkanaが食事をした日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The night of Sakura and kana had dinner",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.8526415189,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1852.6415189000002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "お酒が飲みたいからってどうして普通の居酒屋なのよ\nアイドルならもっとオシャレなバーに行きなさいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you want to drink‚ but why this normal izakaya?\nAs an idol‚ you should go to a more fashionable bar.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7,
      "endTime": 10.098512709000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 10.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "勝手についてきて文句言わないで\nどこで飲もうと私の勝手でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't complain about following me without permission.\nWhere to drink is my decision.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3,
      "endTime": 15.0562811851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 15.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "そっちこそ私に付き合うなんてどういう風の吹き回し？\n今まで二人で飲んだことなんて一度もなかったでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And why are you drinking with me?\nWe've never had a drink together before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "endTime": 22.286773777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 22.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "mihoに話があるからよ\nそうでもなきゃ二人きりになろうなんて思わないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have something to talk to miho.\nOtherwise‚ I wouldn't suggest being together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4666666667,
      "endTime": 29.7096145311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 30
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……それで？　話ってなんなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So? What's this talk about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30,
      "endTime": 33.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "昼間、さくらから食事に誘われた時\nmihoはしかめっ面になったでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Sakura invited us to have a meal during the day‚\nmiho‚ you frowned‚ didn't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "endTime": 39.414467048700004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "なんとなくmihoらしくないなって気になったのよ\nどうして食事に行かなかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was curious because it didn't seem like your usual self.\nWhy didn't you go for the meal?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "endTime": 46.1666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……あの子を見てるとイライラするのよ\n天真爛漫で、太陽みたいに明るくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…When I look at her‚ it irritates me.\nShe's so innocent and bright like the sun…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4666666667,
      "endTime": 52.7911789577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "未来への希望に目をキラキラ輝かせて……\n私はああいうタイプの子が嫌いなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her eyes shining with hope for the future…\nI dislike that type of person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1333333333,
      "endTime": 59.674535210900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 57.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "……それは、彼女が葉ちゃんみたいだから？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is it because she's like You?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2333333333,
      "endTime": 64.36510208440001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 64.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "昔のパートナーと勝手に重ねて勝手にイラつくなんて\nみっともないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Reminds former partner and gets irritated on your own…\nIt's embarrassing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8,
      "endTime": 70.0717912673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 70.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "昔のことは関係ないわ。それに理由はそれだけじゃない\n私が長瀬麻奈をどう思ってるか貴方も知ってるはずよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The past is irrelevant. Besides‚ there are other reasons.\nYou should know how I feel about Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4333333333,
      "endTime": 79.4098641714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈という存在をこの世から消し去りたい\n……でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want to erase the existence of Mana Nagase.\n…Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0666666667,
      "endTime": 84.8966668764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "なのに私達はサニピに負けて目的を果たせなかった\nバッシングを受けて、仕事も干されて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yet we couldn't fulfill our goal against Sunny Peace.\nWe faced backlash‚ lost job opportunities…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3,
      "endTime": 93.1068936348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 93.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "行き場を失っていたところを\nよりによって長瀬麻奈がいた星見プロに拾われて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We had nowhere to go…\nAnd picked up by Hoshimi Pro‚ where Mana Nagase was.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3,
      "endTime": 99.1142178537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 99.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "そのうえ長瀬麻奈の後継者と親睦を深めろだなんて\nそんなこと出来る訳ないでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ deepen our relationship with Mana Nagase's successor…?\nI can't do such a thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3,
      "endTime": 105.44920644769999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "ひょっとして星見プロに移籍したことを後悔してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you regretting transferring to Hoshimi Pro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6333333333,
      "endTime": 110.05333321890001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 110.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれないわね\nさくらと仲良くしろって言われて思ったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe I am.\nWhen I was told to get along with Sakura‚ I thought…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2666666667,
      "endTime": 115.3273015658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈を恨んでいる私が\n彼女の意思を継ぐ子達とやっていけるのかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can I‚ who holds resentment towards Mana Nagase…\nGet along with the girls who are carrying on her will?…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6,
      "endTime": 121.5051484947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 121.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん……様子がおかしいと思ったら\nそんなくだらないことで悩んでたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…I thought something was off about you…\nBut it was just a trivial thing you were worrying about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7,
      "endTime": 129.312584877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "くだらないってどういう意味よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean by trivial?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7,
      "endTime": 131.5773695707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 132
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
